Title: Chapter 55
Writer: Michael Dobbs (based on the novels by), Andrew Davies (based on the mini-series by), Beau Willimon (created for television by), John Mankiewicz, Tian Jun Gu (staff writer)
Actors: Kevin Spacey, Robin Wright, Michael Kelly, Campbell Scott
Plot: The day before the election, Conway holds a 24-hour Skype session with voters, while Frank and Claire stump in key States and try to discredit him.
